 ¦¦ CONTROLS:                                                                           ¦¦
 ¦+---=======---------------------------------------------------------------------------+¦
 ¦¦    Menu:                                                                            ¦¦
 ¦¦    <enter> Choose item                                                              ¦¦
 ¦¦    <top arrow> Select item                                                          ¦¦
 ¦¦    <bottom arrow> Select item                                                       ¦¦
 ¦¦    <left arrow> Select item                                                         ¦¦
 ¦¦    <right arrow> Select item                                                        ¦¦
 ¦¦    <escape> Quit the game                                                           ¦¦
 ¦¦                                                                                     ¦¦
 ¦+---==========------------------------------------------------------------------------+¦
 ¦¦    In game:                                                                         ¦¦
 ¦¦    <space> Fire                                                                     ¦¦
 ¦¦    <shift> IEM (Not available, WIP)                                                 ¦¦
 ¦¦    <top arrow> Move up                                                              ¦¦
 ¦¦    <bottom arrow> Move down                                                         ¦¦
 ¦¦    <left arrow> Move left                                                           ¦¦
 ¦¦    <right arrow> Move right                                                         ¦¦
 ¦¦    <escape> Pause the game                                                          ¦¦
 ¦¦                                                                                     ¦¦
